{"id": 1493, "genre": 1001, "title": "在挑工作方面，你心里有哪些“避雷针”？", "description": "找工作的时候发现了什么会让你对这工作一票否决？或者说什么是让你辞职的最后一根稻草？（题图来自：Adam Avery）", "record_count": 6801, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 0, "image": "img/paper/paper_show/20170210145626GUWcvVioqMJDrQXE.gif", "page_style": 0, "category": 2, "column": 2, "type": "paper", "date": "2017-02-20T03:00:15Z", "options": [{"id": 169472, "content": "不是保洁，天天做保洁的工作?", "image": null, "praise_count": 6, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 927005}, {"id": 169728, "content": "有拖欠工资的家伙", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 898572}, {"id": 169984, "content": "单位总是出一些非职责范围内的任务逼着员工完成，总开没有用的废话会议", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 944752}, {"id": 169729, "content": "人生不能仅为了钱而工作，应该想想自己想要的是什么。", "image": null, "praise_count": 7, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 943582}, {"id": 169218, "content": "出差频率太高", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 771011}, {"id": 169475, "content": "手下有智障，说啥都不会", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 684645}, {"id": 174083, "content": "比他小的他就摆架子，比他大的他就特别尊敬，丝毫不看能力如何，只看年龄。", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 956251}, {"id": 169220, "content": "我们是创业公司，然后紧跟各种压榨员工的规定，好像创业公司就不需要遵守用人规则一样。", "image": null, "praise_count": 590, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 636607}, {"id": 169732, "content": "太过于死板的朝几晚几", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 436915}, {"id": 170244, "content": "内耗大", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 945558}, {"id": 169221, "content": "早上迟到扣钱，晚上加班没钱", "image": null, "praise_count": 793, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 904078}, {"id": 169477, "content": "老板太差", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 894773}, {"id": 169733, "content": "公司单位领导层和自己价值观不同", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 436915}, {"id": 170501, "content": "性格测试、心理测试", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 875168}, {"id": 169222, "content": "\"给你股权\"", "image": null, "praise_count": 138, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 484896}, {"id": 169478, "content": "天天上班喊口号", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1224481}, {"id": 169223, "content": "早上跳操", "image": null, "praise_count": 902, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 780604}, {"id": 169479, "content": "同事或领导喜欢管你工作以外的事情……", "image": null, "praise_count": 12, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 800781}, {"id": 169735, "content": "总是开会 加班 上班时间固定不自由", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 943611}, {"id": 171271, "content": "潜规则泛滥", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 731424}, {"id": 169225, "content": "对于没有什么才华的我来说，只求工作顺利", "image": null, "praise_count": 13, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 924242}, {"id": 169481, "content": "来我们聊聊培训是多少", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 842644}, {"id": 174089, "content": "没有加班费还朝五晚九……还美其名曰这是锻炼年轻人的方法。", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 956251}, {"id": 169226, "content": "天天开会不说正事", "image": null, "praise_count": 445, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 780604}, {"id": 169482, "content": "不给饭贴，不给车贴，还能给什么？", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 925920}, {"id": 169227, "content": "不想给傻叉打工", "image": null, "praise_count": 181, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 942165}, {"id": 169483, "content": "老板", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1208996}, {"id": 169484, "content": "每天做操，团建每次都吃不饱。最关键的是还给你讲指数型发展的企业。不知道的还以为我们被google和Facebook争相邀约收购l", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 942816}, {"id": 169740, "content": "克扣工资还特别有道理", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 943626}, {"id": 179724, "content": "简历要放生活照的 又不是所有人都喜欢照相啊…证件照咋了", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 972719}, {"id": 169229, "content": "工作氛围充斥着不和谐的东西", "image": null, "praise_count": 120, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 352556}, {"id": 169486, "content": "加班加班加班最不能忍", "image": null, "praise_count": 5, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 941533}, {"id": 169231, "content": "克扣工资，事后放屁", "image": null, "praise_count": 57, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 652085}, {"id": 169487, "content": "五险一金", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 736652}, {"id": 169232, "content": "活是干不完的", "image": null, "praise_count": 33, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 528895}, {"id": 169744, "content": "上班时间太长，天天加班，", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 943364}, {"id": 171793, "content": "是否适合自己的性格", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 949347}, {"id": 169490, "content": "老板变了", "image": null, "praise_count": 7, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 942830}, {"id": 169235, "content": "总监上班脱了鞋踩椅子上抠脚，抠完还爱拍人肩膀（一群小伙伴一起辞职的原因- -", "image": null, "praise_count": 212, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 167600}, {"id": 169491, "content": "每天喊口号。加油加油加油，努力努力努力", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 808042}, {"id": 170003, "content": "好", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 943165}, {"id": 169236, "content": "不让上网", "image": null, "praise_count": 12, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 903353}, {"id": 170004, "content": "拓展训练", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 701718}, {"id": 169237, "content": "办公桌电脑旁贴心地放着防辐射用仙人球（手动再见", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 422542}, {"id": 169494, "content": "没有激情却整天嚷嚷要进取\n天天加班没福利\n一出事情找底下的人出气", "image": null, "praise_count": 11, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 942839}, {"id": 169239, "content": "六天班！早九晚九！", "image": null, "praise_count": 127, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 584191}, {"id": 169751, "content": "扣年终奖！！！", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 943659}, {"id": 169240, "content": "老板喜欢上进肯干不吃苦的员工，但不提如何加薪升职，没有明确的帮助员工事业上升的制度或规划", "image": null, "praise_count": 284, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 564539}, {"id": 169241, "content": "哈哈哈哈哈哈哈哈哈哈哈哈哈哈哈哈哈哈哈哈哈哈哈哈哈哈哈哈哈哈哈哈哈哈哈哈哈哈哈哈哈哈哈哈哈哈哈哈哈哈哈哈哈", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 155721}, {"id": 170009, "content": "让我做别的职权外的工作，理由称都是公司的一份子", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 913717}]}